reference_translation: The EU's action, according to reports, is a reaction to growing worries over illegal immigration in Europe, which is now the main cause of the EU's poor deportation rate of illegal immigrants.

original: 冯德莱恩一再表示，欧盟资金不会支付相关费用。
zero_shot_translation: The European Union's funds will not pay the relevant fees, as Ursula von der Leyen has repeatedly stated.
reference_translation: The expenditures will not be covered by EU funding, according to Von der Leyen.

original: 据欧盟委员会估计，欧盟的申根国家去年收到超92万份庇护申请，比前一年增加近半。
zero_shot_translation: According to the European Commission, the Schengen countries of the European Union received over 920,000 asylum applications last year, an increase of nearly 50% compared to the previous year.
reference_translation: According to estimates from the European Commission, the Schengen member states of the EU received more than 920,000 asylum claims in 2017—a nearly 50% rise from the year before.
